News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) Mr Emmanuel Antswen, who was picked up on Friday over a story on the protest at the Internally Displaced Persons (IDPs) camp at the International Market, Makurdi. September 23, 2017 In "News" Few months after the sacking of the state Working Committee members over alleged corrupt practices, a new leadership was, weekend, elected for the Benue State council of the Nigeria Union of Journalists, NUJ, with the Sports Editor of the state-owned Voice Newspaper, Mr. Chris Atsaka, emerging as the new council… February 20, 2011 In "News"